             were indicted, the two first for <rs id="t17710410-44-off235" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17710410-44-off235" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17710410-44-off235" type="offenceSubcategory" value="burglary"></interp>
               breaking and entering the dwelling house of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17710410-44-victim496" type="victimName">
                           Robert
                            Sinclair
                        <interp inst="t17710410-44-victim496" type="surname" value="Sinclair"></interp>
